junction if, in determining whether success is likely, it incorrectly 
or unreasonably applies the law.โ). 
IV.  CONCLUSION 
For these reasons, we vacate the district courtโs preliminary 
injunction on the enforcement of section 4(a)(1)โ(3) of the Act. 
